Turkish Statistical Institute. 2002. Retrieved 2013-03-05.

2. ^ "Population of province/district centers and towns/villages by districts -

2012". Address Based Population Registration System (ABPRS) Database.

Turkish Statistical Institute. Retrieved 2013-02-27.


